headline: Two US swimmers in Rio removed from flight home
content: By Marilia Brocchetto, Tim Hume and Claire Rigby, CNNUpdated 0930 GMT (1730 HKT) August 18, 2016  (CNN)[Breaking news update at 1:47 a.m. ET]CNN's Steve Visser, Steve Almasy Jill Martin, Nick Paton Walsh, Cynde Strand, Tim Langmaid and Richard Allen Greene contributed to this report.
